<li><em>Trifirò et al.</em> PRD 93 (2016) <a href="http://journals.aps.org/prd/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevD.93.044071" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">044071</a>. arXiv:<a href="http://arxiv.org/abs/arXiv:1507.05587" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1507.05587</a></li>
